                    <div class="ttL">Liposuction</div>
                    <p>
                        Liposuction is a surgical procedure that uses a suction technique to remove fat from specific areas of the body, such as the abdomen, hips, thighs, buttocks, arms or neck. Liposuction also shapes (contours) these areas. <br><br>                            Liposuction is used to remove fat from areas of the body that haven’t responded to diet and exercise, such as the:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
