                        <li>Hips and thighs</li>
                        <li>Neck</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Why It’s Done</h4>
                    <p>Liposuction isn’t recommended for people who have conditions that could complicate surgery, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Restricted blood flow</li>
                        <li>Coronary artery disease</li>
                        <li>Diabetes</li>
                        <li>A weak immune system</li>
